Two-World Magic	KEY:Trait ~ Two-World Magic	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.MagicTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Two-World Magic],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.MagicTrait]	DESC:You have bridged the gap between the natural magic of the Mwangi peoples and the refined magic of the Chelish colonists. Select one 0-level spell from a class spell list other than your own. This spell is a 0-level spell on your class spell list (or a 1st-level spell if your class doesn't have 0-level spells).	SOURCEPAGE:p.23

