Adventurous Explorer	KEY:Trait ~ Adventurous Explorer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Song'o					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adventurous Explorer],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Halfling,RACESUBTYPE=Halfling],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Halfling]	DESC:You are one of the few Song'o halflings to brave the world outside the Laughing Jungle. When frightened or shaken, you only take a -1 penalty on your rolls instead of -2.																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Born to the Water		KEY:Trait ~ Born to the Water		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Ijo					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Born on the Water],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Human%,RACESUBTYPE=Human],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Human]			DESC:You were born on the shore, and you easily live on and under the water. You gain a +1 bonus on Swim checks and only need to make Swim checks once every 2 hours to avoid fatigue, instead of once each hour.																																BONUS:SKILL|Swim|1|TYPE=Trait								SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Colonial Entitlement	KEY:Trait ~ Colonial Entitlement	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Chelaxian,Colonial Sargavan	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Colonial Entitlement],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Human%,RACESUBTYPE=Human],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Human]		DESC:You are a firm believer in the superiority of your Chelish heritage, and you cling to your racial and cultural pride. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Intimidate checks against Mwangi.																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Colonial Sympathizer	KEY:Trait ~ Colonial Sympathizer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Mwangi					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Colonial Sympathizer],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Human%,RACESUBTYPE=Human],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Human]		DESC:Your behavior is heavily influenced by the Sargavan colonials. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Bluff and Diplomacy checks involving Sargavan colonials and others with this trait.																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Assimilated Native	KEY:Trait ~ Assimilated Native	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Mwangi					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Assimilated Native],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Human%,RACESUBTYPE=Human],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Human]			DESC:You have adopted the ways of the colonials. As a result, you feel that other, "inferior" races - such as your Mwangi brethren - should obey you as they do the colonials. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Intimidate checks to influence Mwangi natives, but you suffer a -2 on Diplomacy checks to influence them.																											SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Nomadic			KEY:Trait ~ Nomadic			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Bas'o					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Nomadic],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Human%,RACESUBTYPE=Human],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Human]					DESC:You have lived among the Bas'o and know Sargava well. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Knowledge (Geography) and Survival checks, and one of these skills (your choice) is always a class skill for you.																			STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NUMCHOICES=1|SKILL|Knowledge (Geography)|Survival	BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (Geography),Survival|1|TYPE=Trait	CSKILL:LIST	SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Proud Tribesman		KEY:Trait ~ Proud Tribesman		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Mwangi					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Proud Tribesman],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Human%,RACESUBTYPE=Human],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Human]			DESC:You may have to coexist with the colonials, but you don't have to like them. You gain a +2 bonus on checks to Intimidate colonial Sargavans.																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Slaver			KEY:Trait ~ Slaver			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Ombo					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Slaver],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRERACE:1,Human%,RACESUBTYPE=Human],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive ~ Human]						DESC:You may never have participated in a single slave raid, but members of other tribes recognize you as Ombo, and they fear and distrust you accordingly. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Intimidate checks to influence non-Ombo Mwangi, but you suffer a -2 penalty on Bluff or Diplomacy checks to influence them.																											SOURCEPAGE:p.23

