Spirit Talker		KEY:Trait ~ Spirit Talker		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.ReligionTrait	PREDEITY:1,Mwangi Shamanism	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Spirit Talker],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.ReligionTrait]		DESC:You are a devotee of the shamanistic practices of the Mwangi, having little use for the deities of the colonials. You gain a +1 racial bonus on Will saves against divine spells and spell-like effects employed against you by clerics or paladins of Aroden, Abadar, Iomedae, Gozreh, and Shelyn - but you suffer a -1 penalty on Will saves against divine spells cast by devotees of Mwangi faiths.							SOURCEPAGE:p.23
